{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Privacy Policy{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div class="privacyPolicy">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        
        <h3>Introduction</h3>
        <p>Elieb Visions Alumni Welfare is committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal data.</p>
        
        <h3>Information Collection</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Types of Data:</strong> We collect personal information such as name, email address, and usage data.</li>
            <li><strong>Collection Methods:</strong> Data is collected through forms, cookies, and other tracking technologies.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Information We Do Not Collect</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Sensitive Financial Information:</strong> We do not collect, store, or process sensitive financial information, including bank account details, credit card numbers, or other private financial information. Our platform is not designed to handle such data.</li>
            <li><strong>Security:</strong> While we strive to protect your personal data, please do not share any sensitive financial information through our site/application. If you mistakenly provide such information, please contact us immediately so we can address the issue.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Use of Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Purposes:</strong> We use your data to improve our services and to communicate with you.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Data Security</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Protection:</strong> We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access or disclosure.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>User Rights</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Access and Control:</strong> You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Contact us to exercise these rights.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Use:</strong> We use cookies to enhance your experience on our site. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Changes to Privacy Policy</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Updates:</strong> We may update this privacy policy periodically. Changes will be posted on our application.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Contact Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Support:</strong> For privacy-related inquiries, please contact us at [our secretary].</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
